        "TileImage": "$($repository b39cc3e5-3fbe-43b6-a34c-e52cce60273d).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47, and welcome back to Mumbai, India. I dont know much about todays targets, but what I do know is that they are the leaders of the virus&apos;s protection team. Kill them, and a group of ICA soldiers will attack the underground tank and destroy the virus. There&apos;s one more location next that theyre not entirely sure about, so you&apos;ll need to take Trisha Bhas out of the house so we can check her apartment later. She&apos;s working with the virus, but is currently sick. Good luck 47. Have fun!",
